{"tid":1259493,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"要開個兔友群方便交流啦！","createTime":"2019-06-26T14:56:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T02:00:48.000Z","uid":269791,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7096c77f2bd660607a222ccd78cf04cbbb0d4313","tid":1259493,"uid":269791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T14:56:12.000Z","msg":"想開個兔仔主人互相分享兔仔資訊嘅telegram grp<br />\nPM你個id同你嘅兔仔相就得㗎啦！<br />\n歡迎各位兔奴加入啊！"},{"pid":"6cb7e9335708fc4738f18648073acb2e713d3223","tid":1259493,"uid":269791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T02:54:42.000Z","msg":"有無兔友telegram 群？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1258933\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1258933</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"08e5a11ce00af8e924175f3a3b005571fdf3a5d9","tid":1259493,"uid":269791,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T02:55:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NFLVs76.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNFLVs76.png&h=0e8774ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n送上我家兔仔～～～～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85f073f15e5089e628e402d1830222e50f556a6","tid":1259493,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7096c77f2bd660607a222ccd78cf04cbbb0d4313","tid":1259493,"uid":269791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T14:56:12.000Z","msg":"想開個兔仔主人互相分享兔仔資訊嘅telegram grp<br />\nPM你個id同你嘅兔仔相就得㗎啦！<br />\n歡迎各位兔奴加入啊！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T03:32:20.000Z","msg":"怎樣在連登pm?"},{"pid":"a3ac400a173a8e0b51f31d4e2dd2e03475b9deb3","tid":1259493,"uid":269791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b85f073f15e5089e628e402d1830222e50f556a6","tid":1259493,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7096c77f2bd660607a222ccd78cf04cbbb0d4313","tid":1259493,"uid":269791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T14:56:12.000Z","msg":"想開個兔仔主人互相分享兔仔資訊嘅telegram grp<br />\nPM你個id同你嘅兔仔相就得㗎啦！<br />\n歡迎各位兔奴加入啊！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T03:32:20.000Z","msg":"怎樣在連登pm?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T11:48:31.000Z","msg":"又係喎⋯ telegram link: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/MgPj2hVju1CO-GzNYebPyw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMgPj2hVju1CO-GzNYebPyw&d=DodTvzQjJx20NomtZcTkrp2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=4940c556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/MgPj2hVju1CO-GzNYebPyw</a>"},{"pid":"3fc92c143c22ff0f2d91aaf454d50f733dcaa6ff","tid":1259493,"uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T11:36:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>5步驟簡單訓練兔仔去廁所</ins> 🚽</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">根據美國兔子協會(House Rabbit Society):</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>5個步驟</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 請買貓廁所(Cat-sized Litterbox)給你家的兔子(要有足夠空間給兔子360度移動)，市面上的兔子廁所實在太細，只適合龍貓、天竺鼠等小動物。貓廁所會讓你的兔子開心和舒適地跳入去使用，亦會減少𥚃面的墊材和糞便跌出來，更加乾淨。廁所內一半放乾草(Hay)，一半放墊材。一至兩天換一次，視乎有多骯髒:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/28/193323_d2fa117fbe9fecb155be77294e3fc34c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F28%2F193323_d2fa117fbe9fecb155be77294e3fc34c.png&h=fedb6e7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廁所有蓋或沒有蓋也可以, 例如：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8M5RWNF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8M5RWNF.png&h=443fbcae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3FTW7Um.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3FTW7Um.png&h=75001219&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 訓練兔子去廁所是很簡單。糞便是沒有臭味，而且是乾，容易清理。兔子在籠裡大便是正常的，是表示這個籠是牠的地盤<span style=\"color: gold;\"> (但牠會知道litterbox是牠的廁所，大部分糞便會在litterbox內排泄😊)</span>。開始的時候在籠內和加一個小空間內走動(圍欄圍住)，將廁所放在籠或圍欄內，然後逐漸地加一點範圍。不要一開始就讓牠在整個家周圍走，這樣會比較難適應。當你給牠的空間越來越大，可以加多一兩個廁所在牠喜歡去大小便的牆角使用。<br />\n<br />\n3. 將隨地的大便放回廁所內，以及隨地的小便用墊材(例如Carefresh)抹完放入廁所內，牠便會知道要在廁所內大小便<span style=\"color: gold;\">(所以美國兔協說其實不需要訓練😇)</span>。每次牠在廁所內大小便，就給他零食作獎勵。選擇獎勵，不要懲罰。記住不要打兔子，牠們與狗和貓不同，如果打，牠永遠不會忘記，令到與主人關係和信任差。壓力(stress) 亦可以會令兔子生病。兔子是被捕獵的動物(prey animal), 是大自然內每個捕獵者(predator)的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人，但牠們勝於速度, 跑得快。他們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚。狗吠聲、雷暴、消防車叫聲等也會驚嚇兔子。當牠們受驚時，groom(撫摸和親吻)牠們是很重要，令牠們冷靜下來和知道是沒事的。<br />\n<br />\n4. 當然，兔子要絕育才可容易訓練去廁所，因為霸地盤(territorial marker), 絕育後會大大減少霸地盤。荷爾蒙減少了也會令攻擊性減少，牠會活得更開心。專家說絕育後才看到兔子的真正本性，例如: 善良、懶惰、好動、活潑、親人......(有些兔子活潑和親人，有些善良但懶惰等等)另外，兔子是很容易患上生殖器疾病的動物，所以絕育也會令牠們更健康和長壽！<br />\n<br />\n5. 記住要有耐心: 有些兔子比較快, 有些比較慢。當然，有時候牠們不開心不聽話或者些少霸地盤原因也會隨地大便。<br />\n<br />\n以下video 也有教, 步驟簡單:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Rg1RlhtXV7A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRg1RlhtXV7A&d=DodTvzQjJx20NomtZcTkrp2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=acd7e00c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Rg1RlhtXV7A</a> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>墊材</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n記住不要買松木、雪松木及紅杉木的木屑(Pine shavings &amp; Cedar Shavings)，因為有種化學物質叫酚(Aromatic Phenols)會傷兔子的肝臟。Pine pellets或其他墊材就沒問題，<span style=\"color: gold;\">買的時候最好看清楚英文名字 ! </span>因為依然有很多寵物店售賣這類型的墊材。<br />\n<br />\n總括來說，以下的墊材是對兔子<span style=\"color: gold;\"><em>有害</em></span>：<br />\n1. Pine shavings and cedar shavings<br />\n2. Clay/Clumping litter<br />\n3. Corn cob litter<br />\n4. Scented litter<br />\n5. Newspaper / Shredded paper<br />\n<br />\n以下是對兔子<span style=\"color: gold;\"><em>安全</em></span>：<br />\n1. Paper pulp, 即是Carefresh (推介! 兔子吃了也沒問題因為消化得到然後排出來)<br />\n2. Compressed newspaper<br />\n3. Compressed sawdust pellets, 即是 Feline Pine, Wood stove pellets, Horse stall pellets <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n更多關於兔子去廁所的資訊(美國兔協): <a href=\"https://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=DodTvzQjJx20NomtZcTkrp2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=caa2c540\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rabbit.org</a>"},{"pid":"f4c8e44127e21e099d4759d6c83831acd33f923b","tid":1259493,"uid":269791,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:25:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a47151c516a9b73be0203f5378adaf40dfdfd787","tid":1259493,"uid":269791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f4c8e44127e21e099d4759d6c83831acd33f923b","tid":1259493,"uid":269791,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:25:34.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T09:13:14.000Z","msg":"Push!!!!!"},{"pid":"6f4d421a27e048ffaaa179386c2851d125919588","tid":1259493,"uid":269791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T18:56:28.000Z","msg":"Push~"},{"pid":"8fee2a4e13673ef7125633afa4a35ef0ccd315ef","tid":1259493,"uid":269791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:00:48.000Z","msg":"嗯～"}]}